cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CYBER, cs.SE 

The paper proposes a machine learning algorithm for selecting the right customers for residential demand response programs. The algorithm is based on the contextual multi-armed bandit method, which is a popular approach in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with issues related to cybersecurity and software engineering, which makes cs.CYBER and cs.SE possible categories as well.
